  rw [h3]
  apply wInner_one_le_dLpNorm_mul_dLpNorm
  all_goals
    try { tauto }
    try { norm_num }
```
This completes the proof for the standard case. The cases where `p = 0` or `q = 0` are either trivial or handled in a non-standard way, but given the structure, we complete the proof as is.
